Date: Sat 24 Oct 2015
Source: Focus Information Agency [edited]
http://www.focus-fen.net/news/2015/10/24/387304/new-case-of-marseilles-fever-registered-in-plovdiv.html


The number of people suffering from chickenpox in the district [Plovdiv Province?] is increasing. For the previous reporting period from 8-14 Oct 2015, 19 cases were reported, while in the week from 15-22 Oct 2015, 27 cases were registered.

In Plovdiv [City?] and the district [Plovdiv Province?], 9 cases of scarlet fever were registered; 8 of the patients were from the town of Plovdiv.

